      email = "karmanpreet.sukhija@monash.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package aims to undergo bulk RNA-seq analyses using DESeq2 & GSEA.
    After importing HTSeq- or featureCounts-generated reads, the data can be annotated & subsetted as needed.
    Subsequently, DESeq2 can be used to undergo differential expression analysis, which can be used for further
    GSEA using HALLMARK, GO & KEGG gene sets. The purpose of this package is to help in streamlining bulk RNA-seq
    analysis without too many chunks of code being used to format the data.
